  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI&gt;27

          -  age&gt;40

          -  History of CHD or diabetes in any age or BMI level

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant or lactating women.

          -  Active drug or alcohol use or dependence that, in the opinion of the site
             investigator, would interfere with adherence to study requirements.

          -  Serum creatinine &gt; 3 mg/dl.

          -  Liver dysfunction ( Â³ 2 fold level of ALT and AST enzymes).

          -  Participation in another trial in which active intervention is being received.

          -  Any intestinal problem that would prevent the patient from eating one of the test
             diets (for example, gastric stapling that might prevent consumption of vegetables).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
